|               |                   HashJoinExec: mode=CollectLeft, join_type=Inner, on=[(r_regionkey@0, n_regionkey@3)], projection=[l_extendedprice@1, l_discount@2, o_orderdate@3, n_name@5]                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                     |
